        "Data": [
          "<h1>Applies to</h1>\n  <ul>\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 3.6.4</li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1>What to Do</h1>\n  <p>Change the encryption keys at least once a year.</p>\n  <h1>Why</h1>\n  <p>Changing encryption keys periodically makes it more difficult for an attacker to get access to a valid key.</p>\n  <h1>How</h1>\n  <p>Add a requirement to change the encryption at least annually to the information security policy as a part of the key management procedures. Change the encryption keys at least once a year.</p>"
